metadata.name: Aly Ash NFT Zine # 1
metadata.description:
This is the first self-titled NFT Zine by Aly Ash. This image is an overview of all pages in the zine. 

The zine features a PFP of the month, and covers topics such as routines, the struggles of being an artist as well as light-hearted comic images. 

A PDF and higher quality files will be sent to all owners after the close of the sale in 24 hours.
